{
  "stem": "19195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this man says to me, how would you know the Harz Mountains?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, I lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you mean, you lived there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I says, I lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I says, I-- you know Dora, Nordhausen-Dora?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, yeah, I know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, that's where I lived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, when?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I says, when I was liberated in '45.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So you arrived in Dora in March of 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it was all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because those two prisoners who found-- found out there on the floor in the theater-- on-- on the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and they were constantly knocking on the window.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have some food for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's-- that's how I survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was also a Czechoslovakian doctor in Dora who went up in the crematorium chimney, made sure that there is no-- there's not gonna be any people burning.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he sent out to-- to the Allies, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, the-- where they are and-- and where they should go and everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was supposed to be hanged.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was already-- they were talking about-- because we all had to watch when somebody was electrocuted or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to watch that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it turned out that when they came in, the Americans, on April 11, and right away they asked for him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they got together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It is now what can we do for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You helped us so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, you can do only one thing for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Give me a bus from-- from Prague here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm gonna take my-- all-- all my people back there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "John Cespiva.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the-- the prisoners there, the Czechoslovakian, would constantly come and bring me.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
